:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs Thanh H\u00f3a: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u00f2ng 18 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 7/7.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs Thanh H\u00f3a: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u00f2ng 18 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 7/7.</h2>\r\nB\u1ecb l\u1ed7i, click v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/sai-gon-vs-thanh-hoa-vong-18-vleague-2018-372-190603.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP S\u00c0I G\u00d2N VS THANH H\u00d3A</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4037","checkdouble":"190603"},{"date":"14:51 07/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Indonesia 19h00 ng\u00e0y 7/7 (U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-indonesia-ngay-hom-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Indonesia: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Indonesia thu\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 7/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 qua, nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u mang t\u00ednh then ch\u1ed1t v\u1edbi Indonesia, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ea1t b\u1ecf m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 b\u1ef1c d\u1ecdc sang m\u1ed9t b\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. \u00d4ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n, gi\u00e1o \u00e1n \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu gi\u00fap c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 gia t\u0103ng t\u00ednh \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft, tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i th\u00f4ng qua c\u00e1c game v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c r\u00e8n gi\u0169a th\u00eam v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1edfi theo \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng, Indonesia l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t so v\u1edbi Philippines v\u00e0 L\u00e0o. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t c\u00e1c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Indonesia 19h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 77 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Indonesia 19h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 77 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/144642-U19VN_tap67_03.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Indonesia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Indonesia \u0111ang t\u1ea1m d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng A v\u1edbi 9 \u0111i\u1ec3m (hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 +8), x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec l\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan v\u1edbi 7 \u0111i\u1ec3m (hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 +9), U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 3 v\u1edbi 7 \u0111i\u1ec3m (hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 +8). Ti\u1ebfp theo l\u00e0 Philippines, L\u00e0o v\u00e0 Singapore.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua, U19 Indonesia ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 4-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Philippines. Ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y h\u1ecd r\u01a1i v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 U19 Th\u00e1i Lan. Mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 v\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea3o kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, do \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i Indonesia v\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi nhau, n\u00ean U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf. B\u1edfi ngay c\u1ea3 khi chia \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Indonesia, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Singpore \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i l\u00e0 \u0111o\u1ea1t v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn Indonesia- Th\u00e1i Lan. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y, do b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 n\u00ean Indonesia s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u00e1i Lan m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, n\u1ebfu h\u00f2a Th\u00e1i Lan h\u1ecd s\u1ebd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc Indonesia. U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam lu\u00f4n h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong m\u1ecdi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1eb7t ra kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 v\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea3o.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Indonesia 19h00 ng\u00e0y 77 (U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Indonesia 19h00 ng\u00e0y 77 (U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/TRUC-TIEP-U19-Viet-Nam-vs-U19-Indonesia-19h00-ngay-77-(U19-Dong-Nam-A-2018)-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng A</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4036","checkdouble":"190607"},{"date":"15:02 07/07","title":"C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea1i n\u00e1o s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/cdv-nam-dinh-dai-nao-san-thien-truong-nguoi-trong-cuoc-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, c\u1ea3 ch\u1ee7 CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh l\u1eabn HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u0129 \u0111\u1ec1u cho r\u1eb1ng c\u01a1n gi\u1eadn d\u1eef c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 b\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed5 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch.</h2><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi\u00a0C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea1i n\u00e1o s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng 18 V-League di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i qua 6/7, CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc SLNA v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 chung cu\u1ed9c 2-3. Sau khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac, cho r\u1eb1ng t\u1ed5 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng x\u1eed \u00e9p \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00e0n xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n \u0111\u00f2i '\u0103n thua \u0111\u1ee7' v\u1edbi c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea1i n\u00e1o s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea1i n\u00e1o s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/150207-3.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh\u00a0\u0111\u1ea1i n\u00e1o s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi SLNA</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean r\u1ea5t may v\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng an ninh v\u00e0 c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1eed l\u00fd.\u00a0</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 x\u1ea3y ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh Nguy\u1ec5n T\u00e2n Anh cho r\u1eb1ng C\u0110V \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a t\u1ed5 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng x\u1eed kh\u00f4ng hay.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng T\u00e2n Anh cho r\u1eb1ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1ecf s\u00f3t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng, l\u00e0m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1ee1 v\u1ee5n, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i. V\u1ecb \u201cvua \u00e1o \u0111en\u201d c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ecf ra nghi\u00eam kh\u1eafc khi r\u00fat th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t d\u00e0nh cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 SLNA v\u1edbi h\u00e0nh vi c\u00e2u gi\u1edd. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn C\u0110V \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfi t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201c\u1ede nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf s\u1ebd g\u00e2y ra b\u1ee9c x\u00fac cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bao bi\u1ec7n cho s\u1ef1 qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i ra \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec3u, b\u1edfi c\u00e1i g\u00ec c\u0169ng c\u00f3 hai m\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1\u201d, \u00f4ng T\u00e2n Anh ph\u00e2n tr\u1ea7n.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh cho r\u1eb1ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Th\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n thi\u00ean v\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. \u00d4ng Th\u1ecbnh c\u0169ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i cho Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean 'c\u01a1n th\u1ecbnh n\u1ed9' c\u1ee7a NHM b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u00e0nh Nam. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng 2000 kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e1n l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 b\u1ecbt k\u00edn c\u00e1c l\u1ed1i ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 \u201cnh\u1ed1t\u201d t\u1ed5 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch SLNA v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean t\u00e1c nghi\u1ec7p. Ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ti\u1ebfng, c\u00f4ng an m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ed9 t\u1ed1ng nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0y r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)\u00a0</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4035","checkdouble":"190610"},{"date":"17:07 07/07","title":"LINK XEM TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Philippines 19h00 ng\u00e0y 7/7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/7/link-xem-truc-tiep-nu-viet-nam-vs-nu-philippines-19h00-ngay-77.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Philippines: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, link xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Philippines l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 7/7.</h2><h2>LINK XEM TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP N\u1eee VI\u1ec6T NAM VS N\u1eee PHILIPPINES</h2>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://mycujoo.tv/embed/593?id=21175\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen\" allowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe> Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm 6-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Indonesia \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, \u0110T N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7p 1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Singapore \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, c\u00e1c c\u00f4 g\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i \u00e9p s\u00e2n v\u00e0 d\u1ed3n \u00e9p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nChung cu\u1ed9c \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i n\u1eef Sigapore v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 10-0. L\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV&nbsp;Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n n\u1eef Philippines d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u01a1 n\u00ean m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm trong t\u1ea7m tay.<br /></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4034","checkdouble":"190619"},{"date":"13:25 07/07","title":"Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/2/ronaldo-muon-juventus-mua-sao-khung-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Juventus mua Marcelo, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo. Si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo s\u1eafp c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Juventus \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ronaldo t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Real Madrid. L\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin khi\u1ebfn Los Blancos kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua Marcelo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua Marcelo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Cristiano-Ronaldo-muon-Juventus-mua-Marcelo-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo s\u1eafp l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nJuventus \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Ronaldo, m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn 30 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a CR7 v\u1eabn kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, anh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/lo-so-ao-cua-ronaldo-o-juventus-180-190540.html\" target=\"_blank\">S\u1ed1 \u00e1o c\u1ee7a Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Juventus</span> c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o, theo \u0111\u00f3 anh s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 t\u1eeb tay Juan Cuadrado. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 16 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, Juventus d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd ra m\u1eaft b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mang t\u00ean Ronaldo. Ng\u00e0y 07 th\u00e1ng 7 cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mang \u00e1o 7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u00fd ngh\u0129a, hi\u1ec7n NHM Juventus \u0111ang r\u1ea5t ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat CR7 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Marcelo</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus song CR7 \u0111\u00e3 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin mang theo m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf Real t\u1edbi Italia. Juventus mua Marcelo, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marcelo phat bieu ve tran chung ket C1 2018\" title=\"Marcelo ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft C1 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/27/marcelo-real-se-tiep-tuc-manh-me-o-champions-league-mua-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua Marcelo\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCR7 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. Khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus, Ronaldo s\u1ebd tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp g\u1eb7p HLV Massimiliano Allegri, anh s\u1ebd b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Marcelo \u1edf Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMarcelo n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 30 tu\u1ed5i, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra b\u1edfi ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb n\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal \u0111ang nh\u1eafm Marcos Alonso thay Marcelo, n\u1ebfu mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Los Blancos nh\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i cho Juventus l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4033","checkdouble":"190592"},{"date":"14:19 07/07","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! 4 M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca nh\u1eafm n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/26/day-4-muc-tieu-sieu-khung-duoc-barca-nham-nang-cap-tuyen-giua.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAndres Iniesta ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi Barca sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"4 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/21/4-tien-ve-sieu-khung-lot-vao-tam-ngam-chuyen-nhuong-Barca-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf cho Andres Iniesta\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Ernesto Valverde \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p nh\u1eb1m thay th\u1ebf cho s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Iniesta.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Andre Gomes, \u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 qua \u0111\u00f3 thu v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 m\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/hut-barkley-tottenham-chuyen-huong-sang-andre-gomes-172-177215.html\" target=\"_blank\">Tottenham quan t\u00e2m Andre Gomes</span>, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a TBN y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>4 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca nh\u1eafm n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Iniesta c\u00f2n Andre Gomes \u0111ang t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi, Barca \u0111ang nh\u1eafm m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. Diario Gol kh\u1eb3ng\u00a0\u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng TBN.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU san sang doi Pogba lay Verratti\" title=\"MU s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i Pogba l\u1ea5y Verratti\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/day-4-muc-tieu-sieu-khung-duoc-barca-nham-nang-cap-tuyen-giua.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pogba v\u00e0 Verratti l\u00e0 hai trong s\u1ed1 4 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDanh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi bao g\u1ed3m Christian Eriksen c\u1ee7a Tottenham, Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a MU, Miralem Pjanic c\u1ee7a Juventus v\u00e0 Marco Verratti c\u1ee7a PSG.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Barca s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Pogba ho\u1eb7c Verratti.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Eriksen v\u00e0 Pjanic, Tottenham v\u00e0 Juventus c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu thu v\u1ec1 80 tri\u1ec7u euro.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p b\u00e1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Gomes v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro, Barca s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i b\u00f9 th\u00eam t\u1ed1i \u0111a 65 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t trong 4 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng\u00a0\u0111\u1ea7u k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean. S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd gi\u00fap tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4032","checkdouble":"190595"},{"date":"13:38 07/07","title":"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c v\u1ee5 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/26/chelsea-muon-tao-ra-cu-soc-vu-muc-tieu-so-1-cua-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Man City \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n Jorginho\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh v\u00e0 Italia \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli. HLV Pep Guardiola nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho David Silva, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Man City, Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Man City, Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/22/Vuot-mat-Man-City,-Chelsea-muon-mua-Jorginho-cua-Napoli-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n Jorginho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed Man City \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Italia \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i. T\u1edd Mirror c\u1ee7a Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, Man xanh \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Jorginho, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 43 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/man-city-sap-cong-bo-bom-tan-43-trieu-bang-172-190354.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man City \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Jorginho</span>, HLV Pep Guardiola s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. M\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Serie A.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJorginho l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m to\u00e0n n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb xa r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho David Silva.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1ee5 Jorginho</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo SportItalia, Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli, h\u1ecd \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Man City trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Man City, Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Man City, Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/26/chelsea-muon-tao-ra-cu-soc-vu-muc-tieu-so-1-cua-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Man City v\u1ee5 Jorginho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Sarri, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1eafp thay th\u1ebf Conte ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Stamford Bridge mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 v\u1ec1 Chelsea, \u00f4ng s\u1ebd t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a anh t\u1edbi London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, Sarri c\u00f2n th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c Chelsea chi t\u1edbi 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991. Napoli t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 \u01b0u ti\u00ean b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng The Blues t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c tr\u00ean TTCN l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3n Jorginho Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Danny Drinkwater v\u00e0 Cesc Fabregas, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4031","checkdouble":"190593"},{"date":"14:05 07/07","title":"T\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t Man City v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c v\u1ee5 \"h\u00e0ng hot\" World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/toi-luot-man-city-vao-cuoc-vu-hang-hot-world-cup-2018.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Benjamin Pavard c\u1ee7a Stuttgart, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra t\u1edbi 38 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Benjamin Pavard \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Benjamin Pavard ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup 2018, ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Ph\u00e1p.\u00a0V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00ean c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 \u0111\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Benjamin Pavard c\u1ee7a Stuttgart h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Benjamin Pavard c\u1ee7a Stuttgart h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/30/toi-luot-man-city-vao-cuoc-vu-hang-hot-world-cup-2018.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n mua Pavard\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/sao-tuyen-phap-trai-long-ve-sieu-pham-cuu-roi-chien-thang-argentina-421-190134.html\" target=\"_blank\">Pavard l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Argentina</span>, pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a anh gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBenjamin Pavard n\u0103m nay 22 tu\u1ed5i, anh \u0111ang ch\u01a1i cho CLB Stuttgart \u1edf Bundesliga. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua anh l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi 34 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Bundesliga.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. Ngo\u00e0i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 trung v\u1ec7 hay ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Pavard \u0111ang gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Napoli, Bayern Munich, PSG, Liverpool v\u00e0 Juventus l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Man City c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Benjamin Pavard</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Benjamin Pavard c\u1ee7a Stuttgart, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Kyle Walker. HLV Pep Guardiola \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Etihad.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pavard lap sieu pham cho Phap\" title=\"Pavard lap sieu pham cho Phap\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/30/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-phap-43-argentina.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Pavard\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y Man City ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 38 tri\u1ec7u euro, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n cao nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb d\u00e0nh cho Pavard. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Bayern tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Man City c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Pavard c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 22 \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi Stuttgart, Pavard \u01b0u ti\u00ean chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o m\u00e0 anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n h\u00e0ng tu\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4030","checkdouble":"190594"},{"date":"14:39 07/07","title":"Thibaut Courtois \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/7/thibaut-courtois-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Don Balon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Courtois t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019, d\u00f9 The Blues \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n ng\u1ecf \u00fd mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng song th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Chelsea, Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Chelsea, Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/7/thibaut-courtois-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-liverpool.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Thibaut Courtois t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 26 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh ch\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai sau World Cup 2018, hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i anh ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T B\u1ec9.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Courtois \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Real Madrid, anh mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111o\u00e0n t\u1ee5 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a con c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Trong nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y Courtois \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i TBN.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDon Balon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Courtois \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea, anh \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge. N\u1ebfu Chelsea kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Thibaut Courtois</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. \u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea cho th\u1ea5y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Chelsea, Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"T\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Chelsea, Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Tu-choi-gia-han-voi-Chelsea,-Thibaut-Courtois-toi-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh-2.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real Madrid kh\u00e1t khao Thibaut Courtois\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Courtois ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 1 n\u0103m Real c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i chi ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn, ESPN kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n chi ra kho\u1ea3ng 30 tri\u1ec7u euro l\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCourtois s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Navas, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i. Hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang c\u00f9ng B\u1ec9 d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay Brazil vs B\u1ec9 trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi 8 pha c\u1ee9u thua.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Brazil 2-1 qua \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Courtois c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 khi\u1ebfn Real khao kh\u00e1t s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 h\u01a1n m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4029","checkdouble":"190602"},{"date":"15:00 07/07","title":"Liverpool ch\u1ec9 k\u00fd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u Shaqiri n\u1ebfu...","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/24/liverpool-chi-ky-chap-nhan-giai-cuu-shaqiri-neu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Xherdan Shaqiri theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a The Kop. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xherdan Shaqiri mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xherdan Shaqiri ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t \u1edf Premier League trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Stoke City. M\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 ghi 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 7 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, anh g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 43% s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Stoke.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Xherdan Shaqiri theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Xherdan Shaqiri theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/7/Liverpool-ky-hop-dong-voi-Xherdan-Shaqiri-theo-dang-cho-muon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Shaqiri mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Stoke City tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bet365 ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Xherdan Shaqiri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh trong m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian kh\u00e1 d\u00e0i, \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf\u00a0\u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u Premier League \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-chi-12-trieu-bang-mua-chu-lun-de-thuong-172-190422.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU quan t\u00e2m Xherdan Shaqiri</span>, Liverpool c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991. \u0110\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i Man \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 The Kop ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i mua \u0111\u1ee9t Xherdan Shaqiri</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Xherdan Shaqiri theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a The Kop. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Shaqiri giup Stoke vuot len dan truoc trong hiep 1\" title=\"Shaqiri gi\u00fap Stoke v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc trong hi\u1ec7p 1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/24/liverpool-chi-ky-chap-nhan-giai-cuu-shaqiri-neu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Shaqiri\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Klopp \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung phong thay v\u00ec mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh, b\u1edfi v\u1eady \u00f4ng s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Stoke. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bet365 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 Shaqiri t\u1edbi Anfield theo d\u1ea1ng cho Liverpool s\u1ebd r\u00fat lui trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 M.U \u0111ang m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t ng\u1ef1a trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Shaqiri, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 cao, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ph\u00eda Stoke x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4028","checkdouble":"190604"}]}